Lots of broken wormholes: mine, Rob's, now Dave's.

## Symptom:

`wormhole send` and `wormohole receive` return an error.

```
$ wormhole send
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File ""/usr/bin/wormhole"", line 11, in <module>
