4614,IssuesEvent,2016-07-04 14:38:27+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,189798,jirikuncar,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,Citeform: display bugs for references,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_BibFormat', 'name': 'c_BibFormat', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_major', 'name': 'p_major', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_bug', 'name': 't_bug', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],3,"Originally on 2012-04-30

Reported by Michael Peskin.  Example: document 884003.  

Note that references 1c, 8, 10, 23 and 24 look fine on the detailed record references tab.

Click on the link to go to citeform.  

1) Notice that in citeform mode to display things, all of the lines mentioned above (the 3rd '1', 8, 10, 23 and 24) display incorrectly.  Michael was confused when trying to update his citations about why they looked wrong.

2) It wasn't obvious that updating the eprint number in the edit box on the left, immediately updated the display of the title on the right. But it probably should.

3) more mouseover help.",{},{}
4622,IssuesEvent,2016-02-11 10:04:47+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,517546,tiborsimko,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,global: fully functional PostgreSQL DB backend,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_major', 'name': 'p_major', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/roadmap', 'name': 'roadmap', 'color': '009800'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_enhancement', 'name': 't_enhancement', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],10,"The list of issues and PR that we need to solve before we can think to add PostgreSQL:

- [x] global: PostgreSQL Text type compatibility fix https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/3045
- [x] sqlalchemy: PostgreSQL - type Text and Integer compatibility https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3037
- [x] general: fix models for PostgreSQL compatibility https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/2899
- [ ] equivalent function [get_table_update_time()](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/blob/master/invenio/legacy/dbquery_mysql.py#L439) and [get_table_status_info()](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/blob/master/invenio/legacy/dbquery_mysql.py#L471) for postgresql. (@jacquerie) #3211
- [x] bibsort: fix `database create` error (`bibsort -u admin --load-config` return error) #3212
- [ ] travis: add PostgreSQL to test matrix #3213
- [ ] legacy: remove mysql specific codes (see `git grep MySQLdb`, `git grep ""SHOW TABLES""`, `git grep ""CHECK TABLE""`, `git grep ""RLIKE""`, `git grep ""PRIORITY""`, `git grep DATE_FORMAT`, `regexp`, `git grep ""ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE""`) #3214
- [x] DB run_sql problems https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3089 (legacy: tables name and columns name that have upper case on sql queries require double quote, values in query require single quote, table `user` require double quote)
- [x]  legacy: fix run_sql ansi quotes in bibsched https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/3093
- [x] legacy: fix run_sql ansi quotes https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/pull/3096
- [x] access: fix foreign key declaration. #3099
- [x] oauth2server: oauth2CLIENT not cleaned if user is deleted #3145 
- [x] SQLAlchemy: boolean value on PostgreSQL https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3215
- [x]  PostgreSQL: serial id is not update after manually creation a admin user https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3216
- [x]  SQLAlchemy: UUID value on PostgreSQL https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3217
- [ ]  PostgreSQL: foreign key problems when delete records https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3218
- [x]  PostgreSQL: use a passlib to create cookie instead of internal AES function https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/issues/3219
- [x]  tags: error if it assignes value 0 on foreign keys https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio-tags/issues/3
- [x] access: cookie generation fail with PostgreSQL #3318
- [x] accounts: user creation with id = 1 problem on PostgreSQL #3320

