>Permanent FTP Shutdown Notice
>On Friday, December 30, 2016, at 11:59 pm, Eastern Time, FTP services for retrieving EDGAR filing documents will be permanently turned off. Filings will remain available via HTTPS at https://www.sec.gov/. For HTTPS EDGAR file system guidance, see Accessing EDGAR Data.

At the time of this posting, it seems like that the server is still accessible, but discontinuation of the FTP server will inevitably break EDGAR support in pandas-datareader. A rewrite for retrieval via HTTPS will probably be necessary.
",{},{}
