6410,IssuesEvent,2018-01-02 13:46:39+00:00,41007839,ethereum/populus,49922,miohtama,6250754,ethereum,opened,Does not correctly handle Solidity files on non-UTF-8 system locales,[],[],0,"* Populus Version: 1.9.x
* OS: linux


### What was wrong?

