7628,IssuesEvent,2017-07-12 13:28:23+00:00,39940111,lyst/lightfm,440101,dofine,10947873,lyst,opened,AssertionError self.item_embeddings.shape[0] >= item_features.shape[1],[],[],0,"I've been following the examples from http://blog.ethanrosenthal.com/2016/11/07/implicit-mf-part-2/

