8802,IssuesEvent,2017-04-09 15:31:36+00:00,51625787,vatlab/SOS,9889312,BoPeng,20074389,vatlab,closed,Multi-node jobs and `nodes` and `ppn` for PBS to LSF,"[{'id': 325435541, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/vatlab/SOS/labels/discussion', 'name': 'discussion', 'color': 'cc317c', 'default': False}, {'id': 546253590, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/vatlab/SOS/labels/remote%20host', 'name': 'remote host', 'color': 'c5def5', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'jmelott', 'id': 7407788, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/7407788?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/jmelott', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/jmelott/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}, {'login': 'BoPeng', 'id': 9889312, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/9889312?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/BoPeng', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/BoPeng/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",1,"SoS currently allows runtime parameters `nodes`, `ppn` which are number of nodes and process per node and correspond to PBS' `nodes` and `ppn` settings. However,

1. `nodes` is not mature right now because sos tasks seems to be single-node only (#476). The script inside of task might be able to start multi-node jobs but this has not been tested in anyway.

2. LSF uses a different way to set number of cores/procs, so its `-n` is `nodes x ppn`, and an `-R` option is required to span the processes to multiple nodes.

If we stick to PBS convention, we need to
1. allows `nodes` and `ppn`,
2. set `-n ${ppn*nodes}` for LSF
3. set `-R` appropriately in case `nodes` is greater than 1.

Of course, if we cannot figure out how to run multi-node jobs from sos task, we should just get rid of parameter `nodes`.",{},{}
